data.actual_result: User B has the voice bitrate that Channel B enforces (8kbps)
data.expected_result: User B has the voice bitrate that Channel A enforces (64kbps)
data.short_description: Dragging a user between different bitrate voice channels will retain the bitrate of the channel they originated from.
data.steps_to_repro: - Channel A has 64kbps - Channel B has 8kpbs - User B joins Channel B - User A moves User B into Channel A - Repro video: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oAtw3MVo70I>
